mina de almaden rais mercuri price spain 's mina de almaden y arrayan s.a. ha agre with algerian produc enof to establish a minimum price of 300 dlr per flask for spot mercuri sale , almaden spokesman jesu gallego said . in respons to enquiri from reuter , he said hi compani had rais the minimum price for it spot sale from 240 dlr per flask follow talk with enof . in a separ press releas , the compani said that enof and almaden held talk in istanbul a week ago with turkish mercuri produc on way to improv price , but gallego said he wa not in a posit to say what action the turkish compani would be take .